the Anti-Spiral homeworld.

261
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:28,990
NIA!

262
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:42,750
I can't hold a candle to him. In the end,
he overturned every plan set against him.

263
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:54,680
